data.title: Meaning of the name Nagaraj
data.meta_description: Nagaraj is a popular first name more often used for a boy. Growth number: 7. Find all about this name: meaning, origin and numerology interpretation.
data.text:
Meaning: The meaning of the name Nagaraj is: King of serpents .

Please feel free to read what others say about this name and to share your comments if you have more information.

N.B. Sometimes it happens that another name has the same meaning. There is nothing surprising in this: both names have the same origin or the same numbers of numerology.

To test the compatibility of the name Nagaraj with another, enter a name here and click Name Compatibility

You will get a result that shows how much the two names match up.

Numerology of the first name Nagaraj: calculate the core numbers of your numerology chart to discover your numerological profile and your personality traits.

The Growth number corresponding to this first name is 7. It denotes a pattern that assists you in growth and development: spiritual, intelligent, analytical, reserved, knowledgeable, mysterious, intuitive.

Interpretation:

Qualities: Philosophical, Spiritual

Ruling planet: Neptune

Colors: Green

Gemstones: Moonstone

Learn more with our free Numerology Tool

The name Nagaraj is ranked on the 8,968th position of the most used names. It means that this name is commonly used.

We estimate that there are at least 29100 persons in the world having this name which is around 0.001% of the population. The name Nagaraj has seven characters. It means that it is relatively medium-length, compared to the other names in our database.

We do not have enough data to display the number of people who were given the name Nagaraj for each year.
